"Spremni smo za pomoć*!" (We are ready to help!)
"Ćelije su spremne za deljenje*." (The cells are ready for division.)
"Oni su spremni da prihvate izazov*." (They are ready to accept the challenge.)
"Spremni smo da se suoćimo sa posledicama*." (We are ready to face the consequences.)
"Oni su uvek spremni da pomognu*." (They are always ready to help.)
"Spremni smo da krenemo u akciju*." (We are ready to take action.)